title: Ground News - 2023 in Review: National honours await Springy netballer
text:
Summary by Ground News Springvale Districts netballer Lily Cooper represented Victoria at the Under-16s Indoor Netball National Championships. Her efforts at the championships earned her selection in the 17-Under Mixed Australian team, which will play in New Zealand on 20-27 July next year. She was shocked to learn at the presentation night that she had been selected in the Australian team. Share menu More
